ved", "moderated_by": null, "moderated_at": null, "created_at": "2026-03-26T13:04:31.268Z", "updated_at": "2026-03-26T13:04:31.268Z"}}, {"model": "debates.debatetopic", "pk": 3, "fields": {"category": 1, "title": "Pending admin test 1774535067", "description": "Created to test approve endpoint", "created_by": 2, "status": "approved", "moderated_by": 46, "moderated_at": "2026-03-26T14:24:38.671Z", "created_at": "2026-03-26T14:24:28.232Z", "updated_at": "2026-03-26T14:24:28.232Z"}}, {"model": "debates.debatetopic", "pk": 4, "fields": {"category": 1, "title": "Pending reject admin test 1774535089", "description": "Created to test reject endpoint", "created_by": 2, "status": "approved", "moderated_by": 46, "moderated_at": "2026-03-26T14:25:03.905Z", "created_at": "2026-03-26T14:24:50.063Z", "updated_at": "2026-03-26T14:24:50.063Z"}}, {"model": "debates.opinion", "pk": 1, "fields": {"debate": 1, "author": 2, "stance": "for", "content": "In many companies, AI already writes 40-60% of code. Over a decade, remaining work will increasingly be automated.", "parent_opinion": null, "created_at": "2026-03-26T13:04:16.186Z", "updated_at": "2026-03-26T13:04:16.186Z"}}, {"model": "debates.opinion", "pk": 2, "fields": {"debate": 1, "author": 2, "stance": "against", "content": "AI is a powerful tool, but it lacks business context and the ability to manage complex stakeholder trade-offs.", "parent_opinion": null, "created_at": "2026-03-26T13:04:25.443Z", "updated_at": "2026-03-26T13:04:25.443Z"}}, {"model": "debates.opinion", "pk": 3, "fields": {"debate": 2, "author": 2, "stance": "for", "content": "UBI reduces poverty and gives people security to adapt as jobs evolve.", "parent_opinion": null, "created_at": "2026-03-26T13:04:31.273Z", "updated_at": "2026-03-26T13:04:31.273Z"}}, {"model": "debates.opinion", "pk": 4, "fields": {"debate": 2, "author": 2, "stance": "against", "content": "UBI may be expensive and could weaken incentives to work without complementary policies.", "parent_op